[h3 id=BobberyGlitch 
	"Bobbery Glitch
	$LF
]h3
[div class=p 
	"This glitch only works on the Japanese version of the game. Holding X until Bobbery explodes, while holding down R and a direction, will cause Mario to walk at full speed while in paper mode. The game thinks that Mario is in his normal state, so he can still open doors. This is useful for Teleporter Room Early (see here).
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"https://youtu.be/GqgrjX_wI_E
	$LF
