[h3 id=ClippingintoCollisionBoxCorners 
	"Clipping into Collision Box Corners
	$LF
]h3
[div class=p 
	"When jumping precisely onto one of the top corners of an object's collision box, the game will think Mario is inside the block and eject him a few (up to at least 10.9) pixels higher. This allows him to stand on top of locks on locked doors and objects with similar collision (like yellow blocks) and jump off of them to reach higher places.
	$LF
